2017-01-30  Sylvain Beucler <beuc@beuc.net>

	* doc/osx.txt: Notes about OSX

2017-01-29  Sylvain Beucler <beuc@beuc.net>

	* doc/unicode.txt, src/Tar.cpp, src/Tar.hpp: Only use
	__gnu_cxx::stdio_filebuf when necessary OSX uses clang&libc++, where this is not present anymore.  It is
	possible to get it back through either gcc or libstdc++.  However
	wxWidgets builds are made with clang&libc++, and are difficult to
	rebuild, in particular with GNU GCC.  Those builds use a different
	C++ ABI, which wxWidgets detects on start-up and immediately exits.
	If ABI is forced (-fabi-version=2), wxWidgets segfaults on start-up.
	This change makes it possible to compile DFArc on a common OSX
	environment, but the situation annoys me.

2017-01-29  Sylvain Beucler <beuc@beuc.net>

	* BUILD, autobuild/dfarc-exe-mxe.sh, configure.ac: Fix compilation
	with upgraded build tools

2017-01-29  Sylvain Beucler <beuc@beuc.net>

	* src/DFArcFrame.cpp: Fix crash when clicking on 'Package' when
	there is no D-Mod present

2017-01-29  Sylvain Beucler <beuc@beuc.net>

	* src/DFArcApp.cpp: Display exception reason so we can debug

